race.description: Tab (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series 2 F Pr2 Division1
race.comment: FAN THE FLAMES (7) last raced on June 27 2023 when seventh (21.37) over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 6. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. WEBLEC WONDER (2) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a second place finish (20.49) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. TREE TOWN (1) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (17.40) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge Straight latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can turn it around this time. HE'S A PROFIT (8) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.
